# Kubernetes Service

1. Install MiniKube
2. Create the deployment
"kubectl create deployment caching-service --image=docker.io/akarshthodupunuri/caching-service" 
3. Create a service (Service can be exposed to public internet using the type as LoadBalancer)
"kubectl expose deployment caching-service --type=LoadBalancer --port=$some port"
4. Access the service:
"minikube service caching-service"
